options.query:
| makeresults format=csv data="region,place
north,whitby
north,scarborough
north,york
north,harrogate
north,malham
north,skipton
north,dc4
north,dc5
north,dc6
east,hull
east,dc3
east,gw1
south,sheffield
south,dc1
south,dc2
south,gw2
west,keighley
west,bradford
west,halifax
west,leeds
west,wakefield
west,dc7"
| eval heat = random() % (12 - 1 + 1) + 1
| table region place heat
| eval _time = now()

| appendpipe 
    [stats avg(heat) as heat max(heat) as maxed by region 
    | eval place=region
    | eval premaxed = heat
    | eval heat = round(if(maxed>heat,heat+((maxed-heat)/2),heat),0) ]
| appendpipe 
    [ stats avg(heat) as heat by place
    | search place="dc*"
    | stats avg(heat) as heat
    | eval place="dc"]
| appendpipe 
    [ stats avg(heat) as heat by place
    | search place="gw*"
    | stats avg(heat) as heat
    | eval place="gw"]
    
| table _time heat place

|  head 1
|  eval TimeStamp = strftime(_time,"%d/%m/%Y %H:%M:%S")
|  table TimeStamp

| makeresults count=4 
| eval value=random() % (10 - 1 + 1) + 1 | streamstats count as num
| table value
| transpose
| rename "row 1" as north| rename "row 2" as east| rename "row 3" as south| rename "row 4" as west
| eval _time = now()
| table _time north east south west

| makeresults count=10
| streamstats count as num
| eval label = "n-" + num
| eval valuex = $throughput:result.north$

| eval colour = case(valuex>8,3,valuex>7,2,1=1,1)
| eval value = if(num<=valuex,colour,0)
| table label value

| makeresults count=10
| streamstats count as num
| eval label = "n-" + num
| eval valuex = $throughput:result.south$

| eval colour = case(valuex>8,3,valuex>7,2,1=1,1)
| eval value = if(num<=valuex,colour,0)
| table label value

| makeresults count=10
| streamstats count as num
| eval label = "n-" + num
| eval valuex = $throughput:result.west$

| eval colour = case(valuex>8,3,valuex>7,2,1=1,1)
| eval value = if(num<=valuex,colour,0)
| table label value

| makeresults count=10
| streamstats count as num
| eval label = "n-" + num
| eval valuex = $throughput:result.east$

| eval colour = case(valuex>8,3,valuex>7,2,1=1,1)
| eval value = if(num<=valuex,colour,0)
| table label value

|  head 1
|  eval TimeStamp = strftime(_time,"%d/%m/%Y %H:%M:%S")
|  table TimeStamp

| stats avg(heat) as heat
| eval heat = round(heat,0)
